bug.short_desc: virtual gallery in demo crashes after resizing the window

long_desc.thetext:
Hello guys, after resizing a windwow in the virtual gallery demo the demo crashes. It happens when you resize the window horizontally smaller than the first icon row. The error is :
008435 Assertion error! Invalid incoming value for property 'maximum' of class 'qx.ui.core.scroll.ScrollBar': Expected value to be an integer >= 0 but found Infinity!
Page is http://demo.qooxdoo.org/current/demobrowser/#virtual~Gallery.html
Ill attach a screenshot to.
Thanks in advance.
